    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system for razor-sharp throttle response. Power is channeled through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a limited-slip rear differential. The chassis is mechanically sound, having undergone rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. Recent service includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and a cooling system refresh with an aluminum radiator. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the performance envelope remains intact, offering the visceral 8,000 RPM redline experience these M-cars are celebrated for.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
