    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offering a well-maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and daily practicality. The exterior presents beautifully in its original paint, showing only minor road-derived stone chips and light surface marks that do not detract from its overall presence. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the leather upholstery remains soft and supportive, with minimal creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. All interior electronics, from the premium audio system to the dual-zone climate control, operate exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is robust, benefiting from regular fluid changes and a recent professional inspection that confirmed the suspension and brakes are in great shape. It delivers a smooth, confident ride with no unusual noises or vibrations. Complete with a full set of floor mats and a comprehensive service history, this is an honest, reliable example ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
