    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my car and it's been such a reliable companion. It's in really solid shape and has been well-taken care of over the years! It runs smoothly and still looks great parked in the driveway. It\u2019s got a lot of life left in it and is ready for its next adventure with a new owner. If you're looking for a dependable ride that feels just right, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it!",
