    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a purist-spec example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered through a Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term structural integrity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearings were replaced as preventative maintenance. The suspension features a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup, providing the exceptional turn-in and chassis communication the E46 is known for. While showing minor signs of use appropriate for its age, the mechanical systems are dialed in, with a cooling system refresh and a precise, notch-free shifter feel. This is a robust, high-revving machine ready for the twisties.",
